---
source: crates/loom/tests/cli_help.rs
expression: "loom_help(&[\"plan\"])"
---
Interactive spec interview with optional initial anchors

Usage: loom plan [OPTIONS] [SPEC_LABEL]...

Arguments:
  [SPEC_LABEL]...  Initial spec anchors; existing specs are pinned and missing specs are proposed

Options:
      --profile <PROFILE>  Override the profile resolution chain. Wins over `[phase.plan].profile` and `[phase.default].profile` in `<workspace>/loom.toml` (default `base`)
  -w, --workspace <PATH>   Workspace root. Defaults to the current working directory
      --host-key           Explicitly allow ambient host Git credentials and signing config
  -A, --agent <BACKEND>    Override the agent backend for this invocation [possible values: claude, pi, direct]
  -h, --help               Print help
